"20:132:8" : {s: 20, a: 132, w: 8, r: "رزق", t: "رِزْقًۭا", l: "رِزْق", lc: 55, tl: "riz'qan", lb: "খাদ্যদ্রব্য, সংস্থান",e: "(for) provision", b: "রিযক হিসাবে", i: "rezeki", f: 12, rm: "to provide, supply, bestow, grant, means of subsistance. turzaqan - you both shall be supplied. rizq - bounty, gift, portion/share. raziq - one who provides or supplies. razzaq  -great provider/supplier."},
