"20:135:3" : {s: 20, a: 135, w: 3, r: "ربص", t: "مُّتَرَبِّصٌۭ", l: "مُّتَرَبِّص", lc: 3, tl: "mutarabbiṣun", lb: "অপেক্ষাকারী",e: "(is) waiting", b: "প্রতীক্ষা করছে", i: "menunggu", f: 1, rm: " to wait, lay in wait, stick, watch for an opportunity, an expectation, desist from (with an), watch for something, befall anyone, one who waits, one who withholds, or collects and withholds (e.g. wheat or the like, waiting for a time of dearness)."},
