"20:135:11" : {s: 20, a: 135, w: 11, r: "هدي", t: "ٱهْتَدَىٰ", l: "ٱهْتَدَىٰ", lc: 40, tl: "ih'tadā", lb: "সঠিক পথ প্রাপ্ত হ্ওয়া, হেদায়েত প্রাপ্ত হ্ওয়া",e: "is guided", b: "", i: "mendapat petunjuk", f: 7, rm: "to guide/direct to the way, take/follow right way/course, rightly guided/directed, a way/course/method/mode/manner of conduct. Gift."},
